### Use case


For example，we config like this, but we have implicit cluster "al-tt-cn-kk", so opts.Gateway.Gateways only contains "aa-ss-kk-4", g.remotes contains "al-tt-cn-kk" and "al-tt-cn-kk".

```
gateway: {
    gateways: [
      {
        "name": "aa-ss-kk-4",
        "urls": [
          "nats://127.0.0.1:7222"
        ]
